title: Cafe Bocado
typeOfFood: Thai, Juice bar, Asian, Greek, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Oriental, Greek and Thai papaya salads, rice paper summer roll, curry tofu saute are vegan suitable. Grilled tofu can be added to any salad or entree. Marinated veggie and portobella sandwiches and falafel can be made vegan. Live music most weekends for dinner. Specialty espresso coffee, chai and dairy-free chai, blended coffees. House-made pasta.
